channel.title: Addin models
channel.description:
Hey i'm trying to add some models from my old client, to this new client base im using. I added the models succesfully and i copied my models from my old client, into the new client base model folder. After i done that i compiled, then ran the client. I then i logged onto my server and clicked the "add models" tab on the new client base and it said "you have succesfully added all the models". I then closed the client and then compiled, then i copied the whole of the class8.java from the old client and pasted into the new client base and i compiled and got this error.
[code] Errors: Class8.java:10672: class, interface, or enum expected import sign.signlink; ^ Class8.java:10673: class, interface, or enum expected import java.io.*; ^ 2 errors Compiling Finished. Press any key to continue . . .
[/code]
I then logged onto my server nd all the items are the same as before..
Can somone help me? And tell me whats wrong, it may be the error?
